c: 4
v: 140
t: "Gom…óii O Jippinii e mon ka nder Deftere Si on nanii Aayeeje Alla …óen no yeddee …óe jalikitee, wata on joo…óodu e ma…ď…ďe haa …ďe jumpana yewtere goo ko woori nden …óon, si on wa…óii …óum on fotii e ma…ď…ďe\". Pellet, Alla ko Moo…ďoyoowo naafiqii…ďe …ďen e heefer…ďe …ďen ka Jahannama …ďe denndaangal"